2002-09-10 nalin
	* src/pty.c, src/pty.h: Add vte_pty_close() and
	vte_pty_open_with_logging(), breaking the ABI.
	* src/vte.c, src/vte.h: Add vte_terminal_fork_logged_command(), breaking
	the ABI.
